title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Bush trips - backup your progress
description:
Maybe you have experienced it in the past your needed to reinstall MSFS or maybe even your pc and you completely lost the progress of your bush trips. In this video we will have a look where you can find the saved games for the bush trips which will allow you to continue from where you left prior to reformatting your machine.
